<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="52" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,152,618]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,358,511,537]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known from only three localities in the Mantiqueira Mountain Range, which marks the boundary between Rio de Janeiro and Minas Gerais States. The WWF Ecoregion is NT 0 
<number box="[1197,1241,552,578]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52" value="150.0">150</number>
(Paraná-Paraíba interior forests) (World Wildlife Fund, 
<number box="[608,672,592,618]" pageId="1" pageNumber="52" value="2007.0">2007</number>
).
</paragraph>
